Patrick County GIS Pro - To-Do

1) County Parcel Endpoints (Blocking)
   - Gather official parcel service URLs for:
     - Henry County, VA (ArcGIS REST FeatureServer/MapServer, or WMS)
     - Stokes County, NC (ArcGIS REST or WMS)
     - Surry County, NC (ArcGIS REST or WMS)
   - Add to src/data/countySources.ts under parcelEndpoint
   - Verify CORS and public access; note any API keys/licensing

2) Wire Parcel Overlays (Finalization)
   - Confirm parcels render correctly for each county
   - Style layers (stroke/fill, hover/click behavior)
   - Bind popups to parcel attributes (owner, parcel id) if provided
   - Add loading indicators and error handling per county

3) External GIS Links (Verification)
   - Validate links for Henry, Stokes, Surry portals
   - Replace placeholder Stokes link with official GIS portal
   - Add direct “Property Search/Parcel Viewer” links where available

4) UX and Copy Updates
   - MeasurementToolbar Info: ensure copy lists service coverage + links
   - PropertyPanel Sources: ensure Henry, Stokes, Surry cards link out
   - Add brief tooltip/help for County Parcels toggle

5) Map Bounds & Center
   - Confirm max bounds fully cover Patrick + Henry + Stokes + Surry
   - Adjust bounds if parcels extend beyond current bbox

6) Performance & Caching
   - Add per-county parcel layer throttling/debouncing on moveend
   - Implement tile/request caching if county services allow
   - Failover behavior if a county service is down

7) Testing
   - Add e2e tests for toggling County Parcels and link presence
   - Snapshot tests for toolbar info sections
   - Manual QA across desktop/mobile

8) Documentation
   - Update README coverage section to list Henry (VA), Stokes & Surry (NC)
   - Document how to add more counties via src/data/countySources.ts
   - Note dependency on esri-leaflet and WMS support

9) Optional Enhancements
   - Add county-specific toggles (enable/disable per county)
   - Add legend for parcel symbology
   - Deep links to county parcel portals with selected parcel id

10) Deployment
   - Build and smoke test production bundle
   - Validate external links and parcel layers in production
   - Monitor console for CORS/errors; adjust configs if needed

